<author>trjmẗ ạlsẖykẖ/ nʿym ʿạṭf, lḥn ạ̉jnby</author>
<title>mndẖ ạlqdym fy qryẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mndẖ ạlqdym fy qryẗ .. mn ạ̉ṣgẖr ạlblạd
 qd wld ạlṭfl yswʿ .. fy lylẗ ạlmylạd
 fy lylẗiⁿ mn ạlsẖtạʾ .. fy jhdiⁿ wạ̉lm
 tdkẖl mrym ạlʿdẖrạʾ .. ḥẓyrẗ ạlgẖnm
 ạlqrạr- bytk fy qlwbnạ .. yạ ṣạḥb ạlạ̉mjạd
 fḥbk bdạ lnạ .. fy lylẗ ạlmylạd
 2- fy lylẗiⁿ mn ạlsẖtạʾ .. qdsyẗ ạlngẖm
 ṭfluⁿ jmyluⁿ wldt .. ʿdẖrạʾ byt lḥm
 fy lylẗiⁿ mn ạlsẖtạʾ .. yswʿ qd ạ̉tytnạ
 flm tjd fy ạ̉rḍnạ .. mhdaⁿạ bbytnạ
 3- wfy ạlsmạʾ ạḥtfl .. jysẖ ạlmlạỷkẗ
 tʿjbwạ ạ̹dẖ lm yrwạ .. tqdyrnạ lk
 tʿjbt jnd ạlsmạ .. ạ̹dẖ ạ̉bṣrwạ ạlbhạʾ
 yrqd fwq ạlqsẖ .. lạ frsẖuⁿ wlạ gẖṭạʾ</lyrics>
</song>